WEBVTT

00:10:27.942 --> 00:10:30.712
it's going to be hope for them.

00:10:32.354 --> 00:10:34.674
And if you do it at the right time,

00:10:35.879 --> 00:10:37.736
it will enter their heart,

00:10:37.760 --> 00:10:42.873
and it will be with them
wherever they go, forever.

00:10:42.897 --> 00:10:44.048
Thank you.

00:10:44.072 --> 00:10:47.780
(Applause)